creator: WorkLifeLabs
descriptionHtml:
Using the Ezra app you’ll be able to schedule convenient time slots that work for you and meet your coach right there in the app using a high quality video connection. You choose your coach, your time slots and your goals – putting you in charge of your career development.

Ezra coaches are provided by leading international consultancy Lee Hecht Harrison who have been a trusted coaching supplier for over 50 years. We support employees and leaders from 89 of the world’s top 100 brands.

Each coach is individually prepped and briefed on everything there is to know about your company. And as a result, you’ll be able to choose a coach that fits in with your learning style, your calendar, and who is familiar with your culture and work challenges.

The Ezra app is a modern, convenient way for you to access this expert support, helping you on your way to achieve your goals.

Please note that Ezra is currently only available if you’ve received login details from us. If you’re excited about the coaching revolution and want to see more about what Ezra has to offer, please head to our website to request a demo.

title: EZRA Сoaching

creator: WorkLifeLabs
descriptionHtml:
Using the EZRA app you’ll be able to schedule convenient time slots that work for you and meet your coach right there in the app using a high quality video connection. You choose your coach, your time slots and your goals – putting you in charge of your career development.

EZRA coaches are provided by leading international consultancy Lee Hecht Harrison who have been a trusted coaching supplier for over 50 years. We support employees and leaders from 89 of the world’s top 100 brands.

Each coach is individually prepped and briefed on everything there is to know about your company. And as a result, you’ll be able to choose a coach that fits in with your learning style, your calendar, and who is familiar with your culture and work challenges.

The EZRA app is a modern, convenient way for you to access this expert support, helping you on your way to achieve your goals.

Please note that EZRA is currently only available if you’ve received login details from us. If you’re excited about the coaching revolution and want to see more about what EZRA has to offer, please head to our website to request a demo.
descriptionShort: Now, everyone can have a coach: they’re like a personal trainer for your career.
